@NODE copyright   "Copyright Note!"
This software is subject to the "Standart Amiga FD-Software Copyright Note".
It is @{"SHAREWARE as defined in paragraph 4s" Link "AFD-COPYRIGHT/Main"}.

You got this version for demonstration purposes only and have to register if you
intend  to  use  it  regularly.  I  have  decided  to  keep  the  demoversion as
functionally as possible, so you really know what you get! Restrictions  in  the
demoversion are:

   - You may only generate/preview/print ONE project during runtime. You
     may of course restart the program and work on another...:)

   - You may not save/load preferences.

   - You may not save/load your projects.

   - PSVideo-Import is disabled, but you should be able to imagine its
     power. However this is only a restriction to @{"PSVideo(TM)" link PSvideo} users.

To use VideoLab without restrictions, you have to @{"register" link register}.
@ENDNODE

